{"tid":2393430,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[年糕]我屌你老母華麗園","createTime":"2021-02-03T12:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T12:21:48.000Z","uid":51465,"like":73,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7b859431c80acbd6eeaed3839e89674382df0bbd","tid":2393430,"uid":51465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母華麗園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前上佢網訂年糕 約好左2/2收貨 <br />\n咁1/2 佢係咁call我 我返工聽唔到電話<br />\n又無留voicemail 咁就不了了之<br />\n<br />\n之後2/2我放假 <br />\n去到17:30都未收到call幾時送貨咪打返去問<br />\n點之佢話2/2 唔得 想再約我幾時收貨<br />\n咁我都無所謂 但係唔係日日都有人喺屋企24個鐘stand by<br />\n咁我約佢星期五收 點知佢話原來已經寄出左 3/2會收到<br />\n<br />\n好喇 頭先18:30終於收到啲年糕 <br />\ncheck一check發現......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZsUwHO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZsUwHO.png&h=58267ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母個年糕嘅此食用日期前或之前食用係3/2/2021<br />\n我屌你老母華麗園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你叫我點送俾人 就算自用我都無可能一條友食撚晒成個1200g嘅年糕囉仆你個臭街<br />\n諗住你係黃店所以幫襯你(雖然只係喺蘋果度登左一次廣告 都唔撚知你係咪真黃)<br />\n無下次呀我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad57ce0e30d0fb3efe471e1f01c62ceaeef7eba","tid":2393430,"uid":257576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"有冇問佢肯唔肯換貨呀?"},{"pid":"7878d17c19125b846f650f2f60b702e06d9376bb","tid":2393430,"uid":5026,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"係咪打錯日期咋"},{"pid":"5300e450b73ab71ed8b5305a4d74be44357f8451","tid":2393430,"uid":51465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad57ce0e30d0fb3efe471e1f01c62ceaeef7eba","tid":2393430,"uid":257576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"有冇問佢肯唔肯換貨呀?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2